pg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103363/29/1033632982_0:0:3867:2175_1280x0_80_0_0_c32bfed19c90d12856a55a2a2b94ee03.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103363/29/1033632982_0:0:3867:2175_1920x0_80_0_0_8039d1f6240110aeae0c2a0ac77de2b6.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Flickr / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/woodysaeroimages/21798525095" title="伍迪航空影像公司">Woodys Aeroimages</a> </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据安卡拉（人造卫星）网报道：据媒体报道，周六凌晨，机组人员在空中发现不明物体后，土耳其东南部加济安泰普机场共有 26 架航班被取消。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Haberler 新闻门户网站称，周六凌晨 12 点 30 分左右（格林威治标准时间周五 21 点 30 分），两架客机的驾驶舱人员在 2,743 米（9,000 英尺）的高度发现了该物体。飞行员向<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230215/us-sets-up-air-traffic-safety-review-after-near-collision-crises-1107476278.html" target="_blank">空中交通</a>管制报告了这一事件，空中交通管制反过来证实了目击事件。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">自当晚以来，多达 13 次起飞和 13 次抵达被取消，一些本应降落在加济安泰普的飞机被转移到桑尼乌法和阿达纳机场。报告补充说，数百名乘客不得不等待数小时才能离开。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该新闻媒体援引从当局收到的信息称，没有发布飞行员通知 (NOTAM)，但将在未来几个小时内就此事发表正式声明。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 20 May 2023 11:07:54 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/dozens-of-flights-grounded-in-turkiyes-gaziantep-over-unknown-aerial-object---reports-1110482474.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/dozens-of-flights-grounded-in-turkiyes-gaziantep-over-unknown-aerial-object---reports-1110482474.html<category>世界</category><category>加济安泰普</category><category>突厥耶</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Russian Air Defense Intercepts 12 HIMARS Rockets, Storm Shadow Missiles - MoD]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110481483" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/04/1109106593_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_c8bffbad85f40a13f38610badb770e49.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1109106434" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/russian-air-defense-intercepts-12-himars-rockets-storm-shadow-missiles---mod-1110481483.html?share-img=1109106434"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Aaron Favila</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Американская M142 (HIMARS) выпустила ракету во время совместных военных учений Филиппин и США &quot;Сала книб&quot;, Филиппины</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Американская M142 (HIMARS) выпустила ракету во время совместных военных учений Филиппин и США Салакниб, Филиппины - Sputnik International, 1920, 20.05.2023" title="Американская M142 (HIMARS) выпустила ракету во время совместных военных Филиппин и США Салакниб, Фи липпины" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/04/1109106593_0:320:3072:2048_1920x0_